                                 Map & Directions


                                 [hwMap.gif]
    DIRECTION : Hollywood Park is conveniently located just north of the
    Century Freeway, via Prairie Ave., 11 miles southwest of downtown Los
   Angeles; 3 miles east of Los Angeles International Airport, via Century
   Blvd., next to the Great Western Forum in Inglewood.   Short drive from
                      Beverly Hills and beach cities.

